                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作为行外人的闲情科普读物不错 对话的形式容易跟着读下去 谈不上醍醐灌顶 更像是润物细无声 </p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1193653065">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1193653065" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1193653065" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1193653065">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/70884450/">TimeCapsule</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar10 rating" title="很差"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-23</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">全部读完，如果你只坚持做一个视频，而不写书，该多好。可是写了书，就得为自己的言论负责。书中太多的不严谨，对中医的误用或者错误解释，让这样的书泛滥就会伤害更多读者！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1192730112">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
